FT  10 OCT 92 / World News in Brief: Rail fares to rise
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rail passengers are expected to face fare rises of twice the rate of
inflation from January 1993. British Rail and London Underground are to give
details of the increases - likely to be between 5 per cent and 8 per cent -
on Wednesday.
