<HEADLINE>
FT  08 OCT 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG eased in quiet trading with gold stocks depressed by the
stronger financial rand. The gold index lost 21 to 874 while the overall
index shed 21 to 3,082 and industrials fell 8 to 4,080. Anglos slipped R2 to
R85.
